<inglise> COMMISSION REGULATION (EEC) No 1325/86 of 5 May 1986 amending Regulation (EEC) No 3143/85 on the sale at reduced prices of intervention butter intended for direct consumption in the form of concentrated butter </inglise>
<eesti> KOMISJONI M&Auml;&Auml;RUS (EM&Uuml;) nr 1325/86, millega muudetakse m&auml;&auml;rust (EM&Uuml;) nr 3143/85 kontsentreeritud v&otilde;ina otsetarbimiseks etten&auml;htud sekkumisv&otilde;i m&uuml;&uuml;gi kohta alandatud hindadega 5. mai 1986 </eesti>
<inglise> THE COMMISSION OF THE EUROPEAN COMMUNITIES, </inglise>
<eesti> EUROOPA &Uuml;HENDUSTE KOMISJON, </eesti>
<inglise> Having regard to the Treaty establishing the European Economic Community, </inglise>
<eesti> v&otilde;ttes arvesse Euroopa Majandus&uuml;henduse asutamislepingut, </eesti>
<inglise> Having regard to Council Regulation (EEC) No 804/68 of 27 June 1968 on the common organization of the market in milk and milk products (1), as last amended by Regulation (EEC) No 3768/85 (2), and in particular Article 6 (7) thereof, </inglise>
<eesti> v&otilde;ttes arvesse n&otilde;ukogu 27. juuni 1968. aasta m&auml;&auml;rust (EM&Uuml;) nr 804/68 piima- ja piimatooteturu &uuml;hise korralduse kohta, (1) viimati muudetud m&auml;&auml;rusega (EM&Uuml;) nr 3768/85, (2) eriti selle artikli 6 l&otilde;iget 7, </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas Commission Regulation No 3143/85 (3), as last amended by Regulation (EEC) No 715/86 (4), made provision for the sale at reduced prices of intervention butter intended for direct consumption in the form of concentrated butter; </inglise>
<eesti> ning arvestades, et: komisjoni m&auml;&auml;ruses (EM&Uuml;) nr 3143/85, (3) viimati muudetud m&auml;&auml;rusega (EM&Uuml;) nr 715/86, (4) s&auml;testatakse kontsentreeritud v&otilde;ina otsetarbimiseks etten&auml;htud sekkumisv&otilde;i m&uuml;&uuml;k alandatud hindadega; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas Article 2 (4) of Regulation (EEC) No 3143/85 lays down, in particular, that the contract of sale of the reduced-price butter should name the establishment where the concentrated butter will be packaged for marketing; whereas experience has shown that operators are having difficulties in fulfilling this contractual obligation; whereas this provision introduces a degree of inflexibility that is not essential for the purposes of the controls provided for; whereas it should therefore be relaxed; </inglise>
<eesti> m&auml;&auml;ruse (EM&Uuml;) nr 3143/85 artikli 2 l&otilde;ikes 4 on s&auml;testatud, et alandatud hinnaga v&otilde;i m&uuml;&uuml;gilepingus tuleks m&auml;rkida ettev&otilde;te, kus v&otilde;i turustamiseks pakendatakse; kogemused on n&auml;idanud, et ettev&otilde;tjatel on raskusi k&otilde;nealuse lepingulise kohustuse t&auml;itmisega; k&otilde;nealuse s&auml;ttega kehtestatud teatav paindumatus ei ole etten&auml;htud kontrollide eesm&auml;rkide jaoks vajalik; seep&auml;rast tuleks seda v&auml;hendada; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas Article 4 (4) of Regulation (EEC) No 3143/85 sets the time limit for the processing of the butter into concentrated butter and for the packaging of the concentrated butter; whereas the recent unfavourable trend in sales of concentrated butter means that operators are no longer able to meet the time limit laid down without running a considerable commercial risk related to the latest permitted date of use indicated on the packaging of the concentrated butter under national rules; whereas this economic situation is likely to compromise the future of the system; whereas the time limit as fixed should be waived temporarily; </inglise>
<eesti> m&auml;&auml;ruse (EM&Uuml;) nr 3143/85 artikli 4 l&otilde;ikes 4 s&auml;testatakse v&otilde;i kontsentreeritud v&otilde;iks t&ouml;&ouml;tlemise ja kontsentreeritud v&otilde;i pakendamise t&auml;htaeg; hiljutiste ebasoodsate m&uuml;&uuml;gisuundumuste t&otilde;ttu kontsentreeritud v&otilde;i puhul ei ole ettev&otilde;tjatel v&otilde;imalik kehtestatud t&auml;htajast kinni pidada, ilma et ei tekiks m&auml;rkimisv&auml;&auml;rne kommertsriski oht seoses viimase lubatud kasutuskuup&auml;evaga, mis riiklike eeskirjade alusel pakendile m&auml;rgitakse; k&otilde;nealune majanduslik olukord seab ohtu s&uuml;steemi tuleviku; kindlaksm&auml;&auml;ratud t&auml;htajast tuleks ajutiselt loobuda; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas Article 5 (5) of Regulation (EEC) No 3143/85 lays down that the packs should have a maximum net content of three kilograms; whereas, in the light of the experience gained and, in particular, of demand by restaurants and community establishments, the maximum net content should be increased to 10 kilograms; </inglise>
<eesti> m&auml;&auml;ruse (EM&Uuml;) nr 3143/85 artikli 5 l&otilde;ikes 5 on s&auml;testatud, et pakendite suurim netokogus v&otilde;ib olla 3 kilogrammi; saadud kogemusi ja eelk&otilde;ige toitlustusettev&otilde;tjate ja &uuml;henduse ettev&otilde;tete n&otilde;udmisi silmas pidades tuleks suurimat netokogust suurendada 10 kilogrammini; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas Article 5 (3) of Regulation (EEC) No 3143/85 lays down that nitrogen gas may be added to concentrated butter within certain limits; whereas experience has shown that the permitted increase in volume that results from the treatment referred to in the said Article should be increased for concentrated butter with a minimum butterfat content of 99,8 % whereas, moreover, it seems desirable to relax the provision referred to in the second subparagraph of Article 5 (4) concerning the sealing of the packs; </inglise>
<eesti> m&auml;&auml;ruse (EM&Uuml;) nr 3143/85 artikli 5 l&otilde;ikes 3 on s&auml;testatud, et kontsentreeritud v&otilde;ile v&otilde;ib teataval m&auml;&auml;ral lisada gaasilist l&auml;mmastikku; kogemused on n&auml;idanud, et k&otilde;nealuses artiklis osutatud t&ouml;&ouml;tlemise tulemusena suurenenud mahu lubatud m&auml;&auml;ra tuleks v&auml;hemalt 99,8% piimarasvasisaldusega kontsentreeritud v&otilde;i puhul t&otilde;sta ning peale selle on soovitav muuta leebemaks artikli 5 l&otilde;ike 4 teises l&otilde;igus osutatud s&auml;te, milles k&auml;sitletakse pakendite sulgemist; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas the provisions of this Regulation are to the benefit of operators and should, therefore, be applicable to current contracts; </inglise>
<eesti> ettev&otilde;tjad saavad k&auml;esoleva m&auml;&auml;ruse s&auml;tetest kasu ning seep&auml;rast tuleks neid s&auml;tteid kehtivate lepingute suhtes kohaldada; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas the measures provided for in this Regulation are in accordance with the opinion of the Management Committee for Milk and Milk Products, </inglise>
<eesti> k&auml;esoleva m&auml;&auml;rusega etten&auml;htud meetmed on koosk&otilde;las piima- ja piimatooteturu korralduskomitee arvamusega, </eesti>
<inglise> HAS ADOPTED THIS REGULATION: </inglise>
<eesti> ON VASTU V&Otilde;TNUD K&Auml;ESOLEVA M&Auml;&Auml;RUSE. </eesti>
<inglise> Article 1 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 1 </eesti>
<inglise> Regulation (EEC) No 3143/85 is hereby amended as follows: </inglise>
<eesti> M&auml;&auml;rust (EM&Uuml;) nr 3143/85 muudetakse j&auml;rgmiselt. </eesti>
<inglise> 1. </inglise>
<eesti> 1. </eesti>
<inglise> The following is added to the second subparagraph of Article 2 (4): </inglise>
<eesti> Artikli 2 l&otilde;ike 4 teisele l&otilde;igule lisatakse j&auml;rgmine tekst: </eesti>
<inglise> 'However following agreement by the responsible agency, all of the concentrated butter may be packaged for marketing in an establishment other than stated in the contract of sale. </inglise>
<eesti> "P&auml;rast vastutava asutuse n&otilde;usolekut v&otilde;ib kogu kontsentreeritud v&otilde;i turustamiseks pakendada muus ettev&otilde;ttes kui m&uuml;&uuml;gilepingus m&auml;rgitud ettev&otilde;ttes." </eesti>
<inglise> 2. </inglise>
<eesti> 2. </eesti>
<inglise> The following is added to Article 4 (4): </inglise>
<eesti> Artikli 4 l&otilde;ikele 4 lisatakse j&auml;rgmine tekst: </eesti>
<inglise> 'However, for contracts signed before 1 May 1986, the abovementioned period shall expire on 1 September 1986. </inglise>
<eesti> "Enne 1. maid 1986 s&otilde;lmitud lepingute puhul l&otilde;peb eespool nimetatud ajavahemik 1. septembril 1986." </eesti>
<inglise> 3. </inglise>
<eesti> 3. </eesti>
<inglise> Article 5 is amended as follows: </inglise>
<eesti> Artiklit 5 muudetakse j&auml;rgmiselt: </eesti>
<inglise> (a) The following subparagraph is added to paragraph 3: </inglise>
<eesti> a) l&otilde;ikele 3 lisatakse j&auml;rgmine l&otilde;ik: </eesti>
<inglise> 'However, in the case of concentrated butter with a maximum butterfat content of 99,8 %, the increase in volume from this treatment may not exceed 20 % of the concentrated butter before treatment. </inglise>
<eesti> "Kontsentreeritud v&otilde;i puhul, mille suurim piimarasvasisaldus on 99,8%, ei tohi maht k&otilde;nealuse t&ouml;&ouml;tlemise tulemusena suureneda rohkem kui 20% kontsentreeritud v&otilde;i t&ouml;&ouml;tlemiseelsest mahust." ; </eesti>
<inglise> (b) The words 'hermetically sealed packs' in the second subparagraph of paragraph 4 are replaced by the words 'sealed packs'. </inglise>
<eesti> b) s&otilde;nad "hermeetiliselt suletud pakendites" l&otilde;ike 4 teise l&otilde;igus asendatakse s&otilde;nadega "suletud pakendites"; </eesti>
<inglise> (c) The words 'three kilograms' in paragraph 5 are replaced by the words '10 kilograms'. </inglise>
<eesti> c) s&otilde;nad "kolm kilogrammi" l&otilde;ikes 5 asendatakse s&otilde;nadega "10 kilogrammi". </eesti>
<inglise> Article 2 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 2 </eesti>
<inglise> This Regulation shall enter into force on the day of its publication in the Official Journal of the European Communities. </inglise>
<eesti> K&auml;esolev m&auml;&auml;rus j&otilde;ustub Euroopa &Uuml;henduste Teatajas avaldamise p&auml;eval. </eesti>
<inglise> This Regulation shall be binding in its entirety and directly applicable in all Member States. </inglise>
<eesti> K&auml;esolev m&auml;&auml;rus on tervikuna siduv ja vahetult kohaldatav k&otilde;ikides liikmesriikides. </eesti>
<inglise> Done at Brussels, 5 May 1986 </inglise>
